onBordingText1: Find and locate what matters to you
onBordingText2: Are you tired of not knowing where your belongings have wandered off to? With FindMe, you can keep track of anything that matters - from your car to your pets - and always know exactly where they are. Using location tracking technology, FindMe makes it easy to locate your valuables with just a tap.
